      <title>沃伦·巴菲特哀悼查理·芒格，称伯克希尔哈撒韦“令人瞠目结舌”的业绩已经结束</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffett-says-berkshire-built-last-though-eye-popping-gains-are-over-2024-02-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特周六向投资者保证，他的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司将从长远来看为他们提供良好的服务，尽管他对最近去世的长期二把手查理·芒格表示哀悼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffett-says-berkshire-built-last-though-eye-popping-gains-are-over-2024-02-24/</guid>
